text: Emad El Geziry (born 14 November 1981) is an Egyptian modern pentathlete. At age 18, he competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics. His brothers, Omar and Amro, are also Olympic pentathletes. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male modern pentathletes Category:Olympic modern pentathletes of Egypt Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cairo
